OL,3,CHow those in power failed to prevent
OL,4,Cthe violent abuse of thousands of
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FThese were the days when children were
OL,8,Fstill being caned in schools so some
OL,9,Frough justice for problem teens wasn't
OL,10,Fjust acceptable, it was warmly
OL,11,Fwelcomed.
OL,13,FExcept it wasn't just a bit of rough
OL,14,Fjustice. The horrors of Medomsley
OL,15,Fstayed locked inside its iron gates
OL,16,Fthroughout its entire 26 years of
OL,17,Foperation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
