OL,3,CHow those in power failed to prevent
OL,4,Cthe violent abuse of thousands of
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FThe closest police station to the
OL,8,Fcentre was just two miles away. After
OL,9,Frelease, some detainees went straight
OL,10,Fthere to report the physical and
OL,11,Fsexual abuse they'd endured while
OL,12,Finside.
OL,14,FThey were called liars, and threatened
OL,15,Fwith being either hit or sent back.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
