OL,3,CHow those in power failed to prevent
OL,4,Cthe violent abuse of thousands of
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FIt was a reaction that today's report
OL,8,Fhas found was shared from the top to
OL,9,Fthe bottom; probation officers, social
OL,10,Fworkers, prison guards, centre
OL,11,Finspectors - all of them dismissing
OL,12,Fclaims, believing instead that the men
OL,13,Fin prison uniforms were guilty of no
OL,14,Fmore than dishing out a well-earned
OL,15,Fclip round the ear.
OL,17,FIt took decades for the truth to
OL,18,Ffinally be believed. Durham Police -
OL,19,Fnow in deep apology for its 'shameful'
OL,20,Ffailures over Medomsley - launched a
OL,21,Ffull criminal investigation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
