OL,3,CHow those in power failed to prevent
OL,4,Cthe violent abuse of thousands of
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FCharges were brought and the former
OL,8,Fdetainees, now grown men, gave
OL,9,Fevidence in court.
OL,11,FIt was horrific to listen to. Stories
OL,12,Fof beatings regardless of good or bad
OL,13,Fbehaviour.
OL,15,FFreezing baths, heads shaved so
OL,16,Fclosely it drew blood, naked bunny
OL,17,Fjumps, prison guards betting on fights
OL,18,Fbetween inmates.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
