OL,3,CHow those in power failed to prevent
OL,4,Cthe violent abuse of thousands of
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FIt's estimated that Husband raped two
OL,8,Fto three young men per day throughout
OL,9,Fhis 16 years at the centre.
OL,11,FFirst-hand testimony shared with ITV
OL,12,FNews Tyne Tees reveals that Husband
OL,13,Fwould take these young men out of the
OL,14,Fcentre to houses to be abused by
OL,15,Fmultiple men.
OL,17,FOne victim, now in his 60s, still
OL,18,Fcannot bear the smell of cigar smoke
OL,19,For body odour without having to sit
OL,20,Fdown and practice breathing exercises
OL,21,Funtil his fear passes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
