OL,3,CHow those in power failed to prevent
OL,4,Cthe violent abuse of thousands of
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FHusband was offered many chances of
OL,8,Flucrative promotions within the prison
OL,9,Fservice, often to adult jails. He
OL,10,Frefused them all - and we know why.
OL,12,FIt was a horror story, made worse by
OL,13,Fthe report's findings that the people
OL,14,Fwho could have stopped it chose
OL,15,Finstead to look the other way
OL,17,FWhy? How could they? Maybe taking on
OL,18,Fthe establishment was just too
OL,19,Fdaunting. Maybe it was fear of
OL,20,Fthemselves becoming a target or being
OL,21,Fmocked for being 'soft'.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
