OL,3,CHow those in power failed to prevent
OL,4,Cthe violent abuse of thousands of
OL,5,Cyoung men
OL,7,FWe'll never really know.
OL,9,FWe do know though - 37 years after
OL,10,FMedomsley's doors slammed shut for
OL,11,Fgood - these lads were telling the
OL,12,Ftruth from the start. And tragically
OL,13,Ffor too many of them who've been left
OL,14,Fwith unbearable memories that keep
OL,15,Fthem awake at night, the sentence of
OL,16,FMedomsley has never really ended.
